  <description>
    <p>
      Cardthropic is a Libadwaita and Rust solitaire app for GNOME, beginning
      with Klondike and an adaptive board designed for many window sizes.
    </p>
    <p>
      It includes seeded deals, smart move controls, automation (wand/rapid/robot),
      persistent sessions, and a custom CSS userstyle editor.
    </p>
  </description>
